    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m parting with my absolute favorite ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a dream to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my trips. If you're looking for something that looks great, runs smooth, and is ready for its next adventure, you\u2019ve found it! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I know the next owner is going to love it just as much as I have. Come say hi and take it for a spin! \u2728",
      "price": 34500.0,
